Right Tooltip
=============

The native tooltips feature for RightJS

NOTE: will work both with or without the Fx module


Usage
=====

As any other tooltips just specify the rel="tooltip" attribute on your
element and the script will automatically hook it up on load


Options
=======

You might alter the following keys of the Tooltip.Options object

 * checkTags  - tags to check on load, by default '*' - all tags
 * relName    - name for the rel attribute to be recoginized
 * fxName     - the visual effect name 'fade'
 * fxDuration - the visual effect duration 400
 * delay      - the appearance delay 400
 * idSuffix   - the identified tooltips suffix '-tooltip'
 

